column1: -  nil or rounded to zero (including null cells)
(a) Supply of wastewater split by industry/households is not available.
(b) Return flows represents the flows of water from industries and households to the environment.
(c) Wastewater use is the collection of wastewater.
(d) Includes Agriculture; Aquaculture; Forestry and logging; Fishing, hunting and trapping; and Agriculture, forestry and fishing support services.
(e) Households water use does not include self-extracted water (e.g. rainwater tanks, bore water).
